<div class="containerss text-center bg-secondary">
    <h1 class="text-white">Shipping and Delivery</h1>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            Effective Date: Next Day Of Order
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4>Thank you for choosing Urgent IT Solution</h4>
            <p>We are committed to providing a seamless and efficient shipping and delivery process. Please review the following information before making a purchase.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cardd">
        <div class="card-header">
            Shipping Policy
        </div>
        <div class="cardd-body">
            <h4>Delivery Method:</h4>
            <p>Our IT solutions are delivered electronically through the email address provided during the purchase process. No physical shipping is involved.</p>

            <h4>Order Processing:</h4>
            <p>Once you have successfully completed your purchase, you will receive a confirmation email with your order details and the necessary instructions to access and download the IT solution.</p>

            <h4>Business Days:</h4>
            <p>Our regular business days are Monday to Friday, excluding public holidays and weekends. Orders placed outside of business hours will be processed on the next business day.</p>

            <h4>Email Communication:</h4>
            <p>Please ensure that you provide a valid and active email address during the checkout process. We will use this email address to send you important updates and information related to your order.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            Delivery Time
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4>Instant Access:</h4>
            <p>For most of our IT solutions, you will gain instant access to the service and associated materials upon successful payment. An email containing the necessary credentials and download links will be sent to you shortly after the purchase.</p>

            <h4>Delays:</h4>
            <p>While we strive to deliver our services promptly, there may be unforeseen circumstances that could cause minor delays. If any delays occur, we will communicate with you via email to keep you informed about the expected delivery time.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="cardd-header">
            Technical Support
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4>Assistance:</h4>
            <p>Our support team is available to assist you with any technical issues or inquiries related to the delivery process. If you encounter any problems accessing the IT solution, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:urgentitsolution@gmail.com">urgentitsolution@gmail.com</a> or call us at 7408142576.</p>

            <h4>Response Time:</h4>
            <p>We aim to respond to all support inquiries within working hours/days. However, response times may vary depending on the volume of requests.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            Refunds and Returns
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4>Refund Policy:</h4>
            <p>As our IT solutions are delivered digitally, we generally do not offer refunds once the purchase is completed. Please refer to our "Cancellation and Refund Policy" for further details.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            Geographic Limitations
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4>Availability:</h4>
            <p>Our IT solutions are available to customers worldwide. However, certain products or services may have specific geographical restrictions due to legal or licensing considerations.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            Modification to Shipping and Delivery Policy
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>Urgent IT Solution reserves the right to update or modify this Shipping and Delivery Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our website.</p>

            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance regarding our Shipping and Delivery Policy, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: 02/08/2023</p>
</div>